### 查询所有动态定时任务
GET http://localhost:8080/dynamicSchedule



### 新增动态定时任务
POST http://localhost:8080/dynamicSchedule
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "beanName": "print-a",
  "cronExpression": "0/10 * * * * ? ",
  "registryKey": "test1",
  "description": "动态定时任务：测试1"
}



### 修改动态定时任务
PUT http://localhost:8080/dynamicSchedule
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "beanName": "print-b",
  "cronExpression": "0/3 * * * * ? ",
  "registryKey": "test1",
  "description": "动态定时任务：测试1"
}



### 删除动态定时任务
DELETE http://localhost:8080/dynamicSchedule/test1